file.name: account-component.openapi.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Auth Component
  description: Component
  version: 1.0.0

paths: {}

components:
  schemas:
    Me:
      type: object
      required:
        - id
        - type
        - email
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
        type:
          type: string
        name:
          type: string
        family_name:
          type: string
        given_name:
          type: string
        phonetic_family_name:
          type: string
        phonetic_given_name:
          type: string
        phone_number:
          type: string
        phone_number_2:
          type: string
        language:
          type: string
          enum:
            - ja
            - en
            - en-US
            - de-DE
            - fe-FR
            - es-ES
        email:
          type: string

        emails:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string

        picture:
          type: string
          format: uri
        corporation:
          type: object
          properties:
            id:
              type: string
              format: uuid
            name:
              type: string
        groups:
          type: array
          items:
            type: object
            required:
              - id
              - name
              - type
              - corporation_id
            properties:
              id:
                type: string
              name:
                type: string
              type:
                type: string
                enum:
                  - Corporation
                  - Group
              corporation_id:
                type: string
                nullable: true
